{"tid":2084990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"忠誠勇毅警員涉嫌盜信用卡交易被捕　明早提堂","createTime":"2020-06-29T15:06:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T13:36:21.000Z","uid":125193,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"384d467566df9dd3ca64ec770b2a4f0c0fd79af1","tid":2084990,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T15:06:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534770-20200629.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534770-20200629.htm&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTdMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=3ecd0fbc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534770-20200629.htm&h=be890dce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534770-20200629.htm</a>"},{"pid":"593bf663e0b790f213708099102df2240e4036b8","tid":2084990,"uid":125193,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T15:07:26.000Z","msg":"一名警員涉嫌盜竊及以欺騙手段取得財產被捕，案件明日上午於粉嶺裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，早前警員報案指信用卡被盜，其後發現信用卡有數宗可疑交易。警方經初步調查後，於去年3月7日，在大埔拘捕一名33歲姓劉的男警，警方經進一步調查及徵詢法律意見後，涉案男警被控8項盜竊罪及3項以欺騙手段取得財產罪。<br />\n<br />\n警隊表示，非常重視人員操守，指警隊絕不容忍和姑息任何人員干犯違法行為，定必嚴正處理，包括刑事調查及紀律覆檢。"},{"pid":"98b80f4617c59960c6fa2782e8e8e7c8972f0cfe","tid":2084990,"uid":231583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T15:08:13.000Z","msg":"偷水個個又唔撚拉？做咁多大龍鳳咪又係過街老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0787e6c344b3b75c87c27465db403358af231c1","tid":2084990,"uid":71657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T15:09:15.000Z","msg":"官：可以理解"},{"pid":"cd691b95626b6ce7caa84885efa82e9933c32d42","tid":2084990,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T15:11:45.000Z","msg":"情操高尚"},{"pid":"7ea4bd821fdbe3f7a8d77f4ce6464872da636218","tid":2084990,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202